<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <title>HOME</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <style type="text/css">
    @import url(//fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/notosanskr.css);

    body,
    html {
      font-family: "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif !important;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-style: normal;
      height: 100%;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    a:hover {
      /* text-decoration: underline; */
      cursor: pointer;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div style="height: 50px; 
            padding-top: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
  ">
    <img src="/logo.png" style="border-right: 1px solid hsl(0 0% 87% / 1); 
                               padding-right: 20px; 
                               padding-left: 20px; 
  ">

    <a href="/home2" style="padding-left: 20px; color: hsl(0 0% 50% / 1);">HOME</a>
    <a href="/home" style="padding-left: 20px; color: hsl(0 0% 50% / 1);">MODEL LIST</a>
    <a href="/modeler" style="padding-left: 20px; color: hsl(0 0% 50% / 1);">MODELER</a>
    <a href="/history/1" style="padding-left: 20px; color: hsl(0 0% 50% / 1);">HISTORY</a>
    <% if(sess) { %>
    <a href="/logout" style="padding-left: 20px; 
                           position: absolute; 
                           right: 50px; 
                           top : 17px; 
                           color: hsl(0 0% 50% / 1);">
      LOGOUT</a>
    <% } %>
  </div>

  <div style="background-color: hsl(0,0%,97%); 
            padding: 25px 100px; 
            position: relative; 
            height: 10%;
            border-bottom: 1px solid hsl(0 0% 87% / 1);
            border-top: 1px solid hsl(0 0% 87% / 1);
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 19px;
            ">
    Welcome, <%=sess%> 님
  </div>
  <div style="height: 100%; padding-left: 150px; padding-top: 150px;">
    <div style="display: inline-block; width: 40%;">
      <img src="/bpmn-js.gif" style="width: 100%; border: 4px dashed #bcbcbc;">
    </div>
    <div style="display: inline-block; width: 50%; height: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding-left: 150px;">
      <h1>공정 운영 시나리오 모델러</h1>
      <br>
      <ul style="font-size: 20px;">
        <li> BPMN 국제 표준을 사용하여 공정 운영 시나리오 모델링 </li>
        <li>Simple Shape & Activity한 도구를 사용하여 쉽고 빠르게 작성</li>
        <li>프로세스 운영 시나리오를 정확하게 설명</li>
        <li>IT 시스템과 연계하여 프로세스 자동화 지원</li>
      </ul>
      <br><br>
      <% for(var i=0; i < data.length; i++){ %>
      <a href="modeler?type=<%=data[i].CODE%>" class="btn btn-primary"
        style="margin-left: 15px; font-size: 15px;"><%=data[i].CODE_DESC %> 모델러</a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>


<script type="text/javascript" src="home.app.js"></script>

</html>